    public class AnomalyProb
extends java.lang.Object
implements scala.Product, scala.Serializable
    Represents the percentage of the two file sets, good and bad, to have one or several certain anomalies. This is equal to P(Anomaly|BAD) and P(Anomaly|GOOD)
